{"tid":205040,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［峰迴路轉］老母係老豆電話發現左個大陸女人contact","createTime":"2017-04-17T13:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T16:21:29.000Z","uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78c78fe4485a63de5b3d9ff2ebaf1425b2ac68cb","tid":205040,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:16:00.000Z","msg":"話說今晚食完飯，老母順手攞左老豆部電話係到禁，同啲親戚傾下計咁，老豆都冇乜野既。突然我老母問：「喂，呢啲咩黎架？」之後我老豆又要支吾以對咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實果陣我都唔知咩事，因為我坐左係第二邊玩電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我再聽多陣佢地既對話果陣，大概知道老母係老豆個微訊到搵到一個聯絡人，個ID係咩咩「單身女人」咁樣，個icon應該仲係個後生女人黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果陣我已經想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老豆你仲唔死。之後我老母又問老豆個<ins>朋友圈</ins>（微訊入面既一種功能，係比你post下野咁）點解會有啲咁既野？<br />\n<br />\n於是我都諗住開微信睇下咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （老母逼我裝的）我一開果陣發現，屌，點解會登出左既？跟住我再見到佢話咩有人登入過呢個ac所以彈走左我。我即刻心知不妙，改返pw入去。一入到，屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個id變撚左做乜鳩「20年單身女人🌟❤️乜鳩乜鳩」張相仲要係個臭雞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚇撚到我改返晒啲野，check下有冇咩事，入我ac條pk仲要係我<ins>朋友圈</ins>po撚埋啲臭雞接job po,屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩佢hack左我ac冇耐，好似未有人發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我有果啲親戚group勁撚危險架嘛大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪搞啲咁既野<br />\n<br />\n最後想講返句，老豆sorry呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：101%真人真事"},{"pid":"6d27166589f6ca1272adec5bd37c249a860c1d26","tid":205040,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:18:18.000Z","msg":"痴線咁都負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebc8ce66fdf0a18c3f9b5fcdb3b6467a8c314a6","tid":205040,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:18:18.000Z","msg":"信就信 唔信就唔信<br />\n乜撚野叫微信？"},{"pid":"0e83463c431963ecd99cb30fcb2fd8cbae685f54","tid":205040,"uid":83354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:18:56.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"955cc9db35f05f7081f363af15378983e41d3583","tid":205040,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:19:25.000Z","msg":"呢啲on9大陸軟件真係信唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我pw又真係hea左少少"},{"pid":"e7ec0aa36346eaf717835d565b83fc800bf14708","tid":205040,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:19:51.000Z","msg":"ON9"},{"pid":"bcbb618b75fb3e10031013f1d81f5cc99b3c0dd6","tid":205040,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:20:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信就信 唔信就唔信<br />\n乜撚野叫微信？</blockquote><br />\n我好似打錯左做微訊tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef37b5826304ff4fe096539987b581cd67deb194","tid":205040,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:20:56.000Z","msg":"吾你老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4849b00d5626df040dccb687a46ac0f45b6ee7","tid":205040,"uid":33059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB